Brief Me the Case 
An AI-Powered Legal and News Document Summarizer



Project Overview
A complete summarization pipeline combining:
- Extractive Summarization using DistilBERT + LoRA
- Abstractive Summarization using facebook/bart-large-cnn
- Rewriter Module using BART and T5 to humanize summaries

Trained on legal and news datasets (BillSum, Multi-News, CNN/DailyMail) and deployed with a FastAPI backend.


